133
00:09:03,100 --> 00:09:05,120
Tertinggal ketika jiwa keluar.

134
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,730
Jadi bagaimana dengan tubuhnya Geraldine?

135
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:10,430
Berita bagusnya, ia masih hidup.

136
00:09:10,430 --> 00:09:11,500
Berita buruknya?

137
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:13,610
Well...

138
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:17,240
kalau jiwanya dipakai untuk tujuan jahat

139
00:09:17,610 --> 00:09:20,020
