memberitahu di mana dia berada.

150
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:51,630
Aku butuh, uh, salah satu barang miliknya.

151
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:55,320
Tak apa, sayang.

152
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,440
Dia ada di tangan yang tepat.

153
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,370
Yeah.

154
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:07,260
Sedang apa dia di sini?

155
00:10:07,310 --> 00:10:08,630
