158
00:10:12,050 --> 00:10:13,100
Kau mau saran?

159
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:15,540
Kau harus berpisah jalan dengannya.

160
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,280
Kami tunggu di luar.

161
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:20,740
