Oh, sekarang kau masih hidup.

177
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,910
Hanya itu.

178
00:11:47,220 --> 00:11:49,020
Apa ini tempat si perantara itu?

179
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,920
Tempat tinggal temanmu buruk sekali, John.

180
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:51,900
Ayolah.

181
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:58,020
Cangkuk ternak?

182
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,930
Apa? Aku selalu ingin punya satu.

183
00:11:59,990 --> 00:12:00,980
Benarkah?

184
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:04,420
Teman macam apa yang 
akan tinggal di toko begini?

185
